  Title: God in All Worlds
  Locus:
    Page: 67
  Source:
    Title: The Spiritual Crisis of Man
By: Paul Brunton
Format: verse
---
A happiness unmixed with sorrow,
a life unbroken by death,
a health unsaddened by sickness,
a freedom unhindered by restraints,
a knowledge untormented by questions and
a harmony with all other people.
